<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="102" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1437,1215,1314]" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1215,1241]" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Breuning, S." box="[275,461,1215,1241]" pageId="7" pageNumber="102" pagination="12 - 66" refId="ref4558" refString="Breuning, S. (1943) Novae species Cerambycidarum. XII. Folia Zoologica et Hydrobiologica, 12, 12 - 66." type="journal article" year="1943">Breuning (1943)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Breuning" authorityYear="1943" box="[585,768,1215,1241]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="102" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="venezuelensis">
<emphasis box="[585,768,1215,1241]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">B. venezuelensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on a single specimen from 
<collectingCountry box="[1154,1269,1215,1241]" name="Venezuela" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[1285,1374,1215,1241]" country="Venezuela" name="Aragua" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">Aragua</collectingRegion>
). The photograph of the 
<typeStatus box="[367,465,1251,1277]" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">holotype</typeStatus>
suggests that it is a species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Haldeman, 1847" authorityName="Haldeman" authorityYear="1847" box="[836,1108,1251,1277]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Ataxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="102" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[836,909,1251,1277]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">Ataxia</emphasis>
Haldeman, 1847
</taxonomicName>
(Pteropliini), and not a true 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1868" box="[151,240,1287,1313]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="102" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,240,1287,1313]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">Bisaltes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, until the specimen can be examined, we prefer to provisionally retain the species in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1868" box="[1309,1398,1287,1313]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="102" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1309,1398,1287,1313]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="102">Bisaltes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
